{
  "stem": "11089.6",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You will only see my face.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You will not see-- you will see my back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Sorry.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "My back.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "You will not see the face.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "You will only know what happened You will never see what I'm going to do.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "You will never understand it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So if Moshe Rabbeinu didn't understand, who am I, Mr.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Eisner?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Who am I to understand it?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SPEAKING YIDDISH] We have two types of things in our life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[YIDDISH] means hidden.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[YIDDISH] means open.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[SPEAKING YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The hidden things, which I don't understand, they belong to him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[YIDDISH], which is open, what I have to do.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I-- I have to understand.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I understand I must build the future of our people through happiness.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I will achieve much more.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Like in school, you want to teach children through happiness, through goodness.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You will achieve much more than through anger or through harsh-- hard-- hard way of approaching it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that's why I choose a happy way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I am a happy man, because I can tell this for everybody.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I am going to be happy, as long as I live, hopefully.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I'm happy after all these tragedies.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Sure, life is-- is not exactly as you want it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But again, let's take it day by day and be happy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm-hm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only mainly in two schools, day schools, in Eitz Chaim, and in the associated schools.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Those are the two major schools-- 10 years at Eitz Chaim, and 30 years in associated, and four-- and three years in Israel.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So altogether, 43 years of my life for teaching.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's what I promised, and I'm still doing it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I know, thanks God, I succeeded, pretty well.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What I know from students and from parents, I did my job pretty good.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
